PSCT.Base: You can banish 1 Equip Spell from your field or GY; Special Summon this card from your hand. When a monster effect is activated (Quick Effect): You can send 1 face-up Equip Card you control to the GY; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy it. You can only use each effect of "Immortal Phoenix Gearfried" once per turn.
